{"tid":227604,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有一種人好欠打","createTime":"2017-05-03T09:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T16:33:43.000Z","uid":47866,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf190599a650da1c6ffe88d5765a7cfd79d5a1fb","tid":227604,"uid":47866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"套路如下<br />\n<br />\n見你開手機睇動漫,佢就會走過來問你<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜你都鍾意睇動漫</span></span><br />\n然後就會問你睇開啲咩類型<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後當你以為佢都好鍾意睇，之後問佢今季新番你有咩鍾意睇，佢係一啲都答唔出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母，喺度阻住我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7e059f99d9f6f21c9c48565bfa00304d68c8a8","tid":227604,"uid":30745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"咩你唔鍾意睇動畫?"},{"pid":"44a51a54d3670a9aa6daa93a9986901cf9568a1a","tid":227604,"uid":5914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:00:19.000Z","msg":"同你吹下水都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c4a02e3205eb901288c9cf08972afa0b6f33cd","tid":227604,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"問下唔撚得呀"},{"pid":"2091fd9acd1b5364cc8487cc18bda3fadc8a63a8","tid":227604,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:01:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"694dbd31885da7d480b64208c8b5caae14d315fa","tid":227604,"uid":17352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T10:03:40.000Z","msg":"唔識又要黎答爹<br />\n一定係偽毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3a25d3728d424a0d046dc01b8fadbb72882fe1","tid":227604,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0